attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Welcome home to this urban oasis in Boston’s vibrant Seaport District. This 1600 sqft brick and beam loft with 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths seamlessly combines historic charm with modern luxury and contemporary finishes. As you enter this unique space, you’re greeted by the warmth of original brick walls, soaring ceilings, and expansive windows leading to the enclosed private balcony. The open concept living area provides an ideal setting for entertaining, complete with an expansive home-office space. The gourmet kitchen is a chef’s dream featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large breakfast bar. The spacious owner’s suite features a spa-like bath with walk-in shower and jacuzzi tub, complete with custom closets. In-unit laundry, new HVAC system with Nest thermostat, and countless upgrades throughout. No detail has been overlooked! Located just a short distance to some of the city’s best restaurants, shops, entertainment, and easy access to 93 & South Station.
